Sunset across the Santa Monica Bay, from the bike path in Manhattan Beach.
</p>

<p class="jp">   
<span class="title_jp">マンハッタンの夕日 </span>
 
マンハッタン・ビーチの自転車道から、サンタモニカ湾の向こうに沈む夕日。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Manhattan Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Strand" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Sunset across the Santa Monica Bay, from the bike path in Manhattan Beach.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2307_A7R09329.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2307_A7R09329.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Golden Strand</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230712/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Golden Strand" /><published>2023-07-12T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2023-07-12T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/golden-strand</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230712/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Golden hour on the Strand in Manhattan Beach. This section of the Strand has two paths; one below for riding; one above for walking, or just admiring the sunset.
</p>

<p class="jp">   
<span class="title_jp">金色なストランド</span>
マンハッタン・ビーチのストランドでマジックアワー。</p>
<p class="jp"> 
ストランドのこの部分には2つの道があり、ひとつは自転車用、もうひとつは散歩用、あるいはただ夕日を眺めるためのものだ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Manhattan Beach" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><category term="Strand" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Golden hour on the Strand in Manhattan Beach. This section of the Strand has two paths; one below for riding; one above for walking, or just admiring the sunset.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2307_A7R09320.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2307_A7R09320.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Redondo Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230708/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Redondo Sunset" /><published>2023-07-08T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2023-07-08T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/redondo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230708/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Sailboat returns to the Redondo Beach Harbor, as the sun sets behind the Redondo Beach Pier.</p>

<p class="jp">   
レドンド・ビーチ桟橋の向こうに夕日が沈む中、レドンド・ビーチ・マリーナに戻るヨット。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Boats" /><category term="Piers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Sailboat returns to the Redondo Beach Harbor, as the sun sets behind the Redondo Beach Pier.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2307_A7R09213-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2307_A7R09213-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Bird of Paradise</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230706/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Bird of Paradise" /><published>2023-07-06T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2023-07-06T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/paradise</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230706/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Beautiful flower in bloom on the street in Hermosa Beach.
</p>

<p class="jp">   
	<span class="title_jp">風鳥</span>
ハーモサ・ビーチの通りに咲いた美しい花。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Beautiful flower in bloom on the street in Hermosa Beach.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2307_A7R09133.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2307_A7R09133.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hermosa Summer</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230705/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hermosa Summer" /><published>2023-07-05T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2023-07-05T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/Hermosa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230705/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Warm day at the beach. Looking north from the Hermosa Beach Pier.
</p>

<p class="jp">   
	<span class="title_jp">ハーモサ（美しい）夏</span>
暖かい日のビーチ。ハーモサ・ビーチの桟橋から北を見る。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Warm day at the beach. Looking north from the Hermosa Beach Pier.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2307_A7R09094-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2307_A7R09094-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Apple Store at The Grove</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230629/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Apple Store at The Grove" /><published>2023-06-29T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2023-06-29T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/apple</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230629/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Dad takes his girls into the Apple Store. Opened in 2021, this was my first time to this tall box of a store, with ficus trees, a huge, mirrored ceiling, and skylights at the edges. It’s almost like being outside. </p>
<p class="en">Almost completely lit with natural light, and with the trees creating oxygen, I’d guess its pretty eco-friendly.</p>

<p class="jp">    
お父さんが娘たちをアップルストアに連れて行く。2021年にオープンしたこの店に行くのは初めてだった。とても背の高い箱で、中には榕樹の木があり、鏡張りの巨大な天井があり、側面には天窓がある。まるで外にいるようだ。</p>

<p class="jp"> 
ほぼ完全に自然光で照らされ、木々が酸素を作り出しているので、かなりエコだと思う。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hollywood" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Dad takes his girls into the Apple Store. Opened in 2021, this was my first time to this tall box of a store, with ficus trees, a huge, mirrored ceiling, and skylights at the edges. It’s almost like being outside. Almost completely lit with natural light, and with the trees creating oxygen, I’d guess its pretty eco-friendly.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2306_IMG_1697.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2306_IMG_1697.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hollywood</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230628/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hollywood" /><published>2023-06-28T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2023-06-28T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hollywood</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230628/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The iconic Hollywood sign looking over downtown Hollywood.
</p>

<p class="jp">    
ハリウッドのダウンタウンを見下ろす象徴的なハリウッド・サイン。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hollywood" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The iconic Hollywood sign looking over downtown Hollywood.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2306_A7R09042.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2306_A7R09042.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Bluff Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230627/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Bluff Sunset" /><published>2023-06-27T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2023-06-27T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/bluff-sunset</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230627/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
