</p>

<p class="jp">    
<span class="title_jp">断崖の夕日</span>
<a href="/230626/">前の写真</a>で断崖を照らしていた夕日だ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Here is the sunset that was illuminating the bluff in the previous photo.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2306_A7R08921-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2306_A7R08921-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Bluff Cove</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230626/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Bluff Cove" /><published>2023-06-26T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2023-06-26T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/bluff-cove</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230626/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The setting sun bathes the cliffs above Bluff Cove in a golden light.
</p>

<p class="jp">    
夕日がブラフ・コーブの上の崖を黄金色に照らす。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Foliage" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The setting sun bathes the cliffs above Bluff Cove in a golden light.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2306_A7R08887-Pano.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2306_A7R08887-Pano.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Summer Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230623/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Summer Sunset" /><published>2023-06-23T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2023-06-23T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/summer-sunset</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230623/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
As we pass the summer solstice, the sun sets very far north, over Malibu. 
</p>

<p class="jp">    
<span class="title_jp">夏の日没</span>
夏至が過ぎると、太陽はマリブの北に沈む。


</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Lifeguard Towers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[As we pass the summer solstice, the sun sets very far north, over Malibu.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2306_A7R08842.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2306_A7R08842.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>